163
00:10:11,311 --> 00:10:13,745
She's a wonderful girl
and she really likes you.

164
00:10:14,147 --> 00:10:18,641
- I know, but she's not you.
- I'm not me.

165
00:10:19,319 --> 00:10:22,516
