196
00:12:11,764 --> 00:12:13,254
Sheldon, what you need to do...

197
00:12:13,433 --> 00:12:17,563
...is figure out a way
to exact vengeance on Kripke, like...

198
00:12:18,071 --> 00:12:20,039
